internal.content:
---
title: Contribute
description: The report an issue content goes here!
---

import { OutboundLink } from "gatsby-plugin-google-analytics"

<PageDescription>
<Row>
<Column colMd={5} colLg={8}>

Though we have put our best effort at curating the dataset, it is possible that you have a great idea to enhance it further or you've discovered an error.

<InlineNotification kind="warning">
Warning: We welcome your contributions. However, please do not attach any data files when raising the GitHub issues.
</InlineNotification>

</Column>
<Column colMd={2} colLg={3} offsetMd={1} offsetLg={1}>
<Aside aria-label="Link aside">

<InlineNotification kind="success">
<OutboundLink href="https://github.com/IBM/wntrac/blob/master/data/README.md" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Download the latest dataset</OutboundLink>
</InlineNotification>

</Aside>

</Column>
</Row>
</PageDescription>

## Request a feature

If you find that the dataset is missing some NPI events or could be enhanced with more data elements,
please use <OutboundLink href="https://github.com/IBM/wntrac/issues/new?assignees=&labels=enhancement&template=enhancement-reporting-template.md&title=" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">this</OutboundLink>
GitHub issue template to report.

## Report an error

If you find an error in the dataset, please use <OutboundLink href="https://github.com/IBM/wntrac/issues/new?assignees=&labels=error&template=error-reporting-template.md&title=" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">this</OutboundLink>
GitHub issue template to report for each
error individually. We appreciate your help in fixing these issues.
